Name: Egg Over It: Fall Flat From the Top
About the game: WELCOME TO THIS ADVENTURE Take on a real tactical jumping adventure with Egg Over It!!! A challenge where you will have to lift the egg to the top in search of its origin, but explore carefully; a single failed jump could lead to a long fall. Guide it through sewers, buildings, aerial vehicles and skyscrapers. FEATURES Climb the egg to the top. Perform aerial moves. Walk to be more precise. Play using only impulses. A LITTLE MORE ABOUT EGG OVER IT Avoid making a wrong move or you will fall into the sewers starting from the beginning. Remember that the egg is ovoid, so its shape may play a trick on you. See the scenery with a day and night cycle. Enjoy the most Andalusian music composed with Spanish guitar. Let the game's narration envelop you during the game. Illo, will you have the balls to beat this game? Download Egg Over it now, a game where the only way to advance is up.
